isPhoneNumber

public static boolean isPhoneNumber(String str)

Validating for phone number.

e.g.
  • 78674585 --> valid
  • 6872-4585 --> valid
  • (6872)4585 --> valid
  • 0086-10-6872-4585 --> valid
  • 0086-(10)-6872-4585 --> invalid
  • 0086(10)68724585 --> invalid

    • 参数：
    str - string to be validated
    返回：
    If the str is valid phone number return true, otherwise return false.
